interpretation: The "man guard" card depicts a stoic and protective figure, ready to defend and keep watch. This card may indicate a need for increased security and protection in your life, or the need to be more vigilant and cautious. Alternatively, this card may represent a person in your life who serves as a protector or authority figure, such as a police officer or military personnel. The "man guard" card can also signify a need for discipline and structure, or a desire for a sense of order and stability. Keywords associated with this card include protection, security, vigilance, authority, discipline, and structure.
